                     <interp inst="t18370612-1578-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18370612-cd-166" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370612-1578-offence-1 t18370612-cd-166"></join>12 of June</rs>, at <placeName id="t18370612-geo-11">
