                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1578-18370612 t18370612-1578-punishment-158"></join>Canfined One Year in the Peniteniary</rs>, and then 
<rs id="t18370612-1578-punishment-159" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18370612-1578-punishment-159" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1578-18370612 t18370612-1578-punishment-159"></join>Transported for Life</rs>.—(<hi rend="italic">Strongly recommended to mercy by the Prosecutor and Jury, on account of the sudden temptation, and his being anxious to deliver up the property.</hi>)</p>
